   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> New Athelfi</span><hr size=1> Alysia turned her eyes from her scrolls as she studied the past of the Greecian Amazon life. She wanted to know and remember all she could from her life before.<br><br><br>She stood hearing noise burrowing outside her hut. She walked out into the day light and looked at the Amazon. She looked at her attire and saw that she was an initiate seeing she had yet to recieve a Scynthian Medallion.<br><br>&quot;You must be Varia?&quot;<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 71<br> <font color=#993300>(1/28/02 5:50:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/yakut.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Yakut.</span><hr size=1> Yakut made her way into Scynthia. She walked further into the village of Scynthia stopping at the Queen's Hut to see Aly/Samasara. Baby Glory was with her, the child now looking 8 months old. Glory was an Amazon Mystic and grew quickly.<br><br>&quot;Yasoo Vasilissa.&quot;<br><br>Yakut smiled to Aly/Samsara then to Varia.<br><br>&quot;Yasoo Varia.&quot;  <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§Amazon Queen, Amazon Shamaness, and Amazon Mother...Your good old Northern Amazon!</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugabrielleofthechakram.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gabrielle of the Chakram</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#993300>(1/28/02 6:05:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/gabrielle.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Gabby joined the fray.</span><hr size=1> Gabrielle rode in on her horse Sapphire and stabled him she walked around Scynthia a bit til Yakut and Var were done with the Queen. She wanted to talk with Var and Yakut when they were done. <p>§Gabrielle§<BR>¤Amazon Queen¤ <BR>¤Warrior Bard¤ <BR>¤Battling Bard of Potediea¤<BR> "Peace is worth fighting for!"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/tsianina2.bmp" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 217<br> <font color=#993300>(1/28/02 9:36:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/tjcontenderpremiere.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gabby joined the fray.</span><hr size=1> ~Yasoo Yakut,~ Varia said and nodded, then turned back to Alysia. ~Yes, I'm Varia. We met a few times back when... erm... a while back.~ She smiled.<br><br>(has Var met this Gabby before?) <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT" size="+1"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 302<br> <font color=#993300>(1/29/02 3:31:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Pack of Wolves</span><hr size=1> As the sisters came closer to the Queen, two large wolves met at her side. Aeceus and Scythe. <br><br>She smiled to them and then looked to the three Amazons.<br><br>&quot;Yasoo to you all. Forgive me of my lost senses, but whom of you have I met previously and under what circumstances?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 76<br> <font color=#993300>(1/29/02 6:17:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/yakut.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Yakut</span><hr size=1> &quot;Vasilissa, it is I, Yakut: Amazon Queen of Tanais River Valley and Shamaness of the North. I came here with great news. I am friend of yours. My Lands are right next door to Scynthia.&quot;<br><br>Yakut didn't quite understand how Aly/Samsara could lose her memory while coming back. Did something go wrong in the ritual or was it supposed to be this way? Yakut missed the old Aly. The old Aly was someone Yakut could always trust and someone who had shared her happiness when Yakut's daughters were born and whatever else good would happen.<br><br>&quot;I am to be married. Belle, I mean,  Princess Isabelle has agreed to do the ceremony.&quot;<br><br>Samsara was merciless. Yakut was uneasy around such sisters. Which was even more odd because Alysia had always been a great friend of Yakut. Alysia and Belle were like family.<br><br>(OOC- No Var-MUN, Thats why Gabby wants to see Var to meet her) <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§Amazon Queen, Amazon Shamaness, and Amazon Mother...Your good old Northern Amazon!</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/29/02 6:19:46 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 303<br> <font color=#993300>(1/30/02 1:02:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Yakut</span><hr size=1> Alysia smiled lightly to Yakut. She trusted Yakut being a Northern Amazon and a Queen.<br><br>&quot;I give you congradulations upon your ceremony.&quot;<br><br>She blinked for a moment at the mention of Belle and then nodded realising.<br><br>&quot;Oh you mean Karina! I mean . . . Belle yes Belle.&quot;<br><br>Things were still a little hazy. She was regaining things, but slowly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/tsianina2.bmp" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 221<br> <font color=#993300>(1/31/02 2:25:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/tjcontenderpremiere.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Var</span><hr size=1> Varia looked at Alysia. ~Um... we met when an ilithios was trying to attack your village with his pathetic fire-breathing animal... and Dawn and I were having a sort of argument...~ she just stood there looking at Alysia, wondering how on earth she could forget her entire past, since she didn't know about the whole Samsara/death thingy. <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT" size="+1"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usartha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sartha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#993300>(1/31/02 8:44:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=213.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sar watching over</span><hr size=1> ::Sartha, in all her ghostliness, could not be seen as she watched them, but her presence could be sensed if a person were &quot;reaching&quot; in that way. She was leaning against one wall as always, arms crossed. She had come for a little ghost-happy visit and had stepped into the present conversation. She had learned of Aly/Samsara's situation for her otherworldly sights. If anyone could sense her, it would be Aly/Samsara. She had never been very close to the Amazon Queen when she was Aly, but they had shared moments as warriors and Amazons. She simply stood there and watched, silvery-golden eyes observing as they always had before her death:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 widt